        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JC for the gift of his book [<hi rend="italic">A primer of art</hi> (1882)]. Wishes JC could explain why certain lines and figures give pleasure.</p>  
<p>Comments on Huxley’s essays on Priestley and [animal] automatism [<hi rend="italic">Science and culture and other essays</hi> (1881)].</p> 
            <p>JC’s portrait [of CD] is much admired.</p>
        </abstract>
